# Run Arguments and Experiment Commands

Date captured: 2026-03-14

## 1) QuixBugs (v5) - Script Arguments and How Experiments Were Run

Script:
- `src/step6_orchestrator_quixbugs_v5_attempts.py`

Required arguments:
- `--tasks_path` (JSONL task manifest path)
- `--task_index` (0-based task row index)
- `--llama_path` (llama CLI path, typically `/usr/local/bin/llama-completion`)
- `--gguf_model_path` (GGUF model file path)

Optional arguments (defaults from code):
- `--max_attempts` (default `5`)
- `--slm_timeout_s` (default `900`)
- `--slm_max_output_mb` (default `8`)
- `--skip_rollback` (flag; default off)
- `--fallback_model` (default empty string, fallback disabled)
- `--fallback_max_attempts` (default `2`)
- `--fallback_timeout_s` (default `120`)
- `--fallback_max_new_tokens` (default `1200`)
- `--fallback_temp` (default `0.0`)
- `--repo_root` (default `"."`)

Notes:
- The test command and buggy file path are read from the selected row in `--tasks_path`.
- Per task logic enforces a minimum test timeout of 10 seconds from task metadata (`max(task_timeout, 10)`).
- If `--fallback_model` is set, `OPENAI_API_KEY` must exist in environment.

Typical experiment run (single task, SLM + fallback):
```bash
python src/step6_orchestrator_quixbugs_v5_attempts.py \
  --tasks_path data/quixbugs_tasks_v2.jsonl \
  --task_index 0 \
  --llama_path /usr/local/bin/llama-completion \
  --gguf_model_path models/gguf/qwen2.5-coder-1.5b-instruct-q4_k_m.gguf \
  --max_attempts 3 \
  --slm_timeout_s 400 \
  --fallback_model gpt-4.1 \
  --fallback_max_attempts 2 \
  --fallback_timeout_s 120 \
  --repo_root .
```

Typical batch pattern:
```bash
for i in $(seq 0 40); do
  python src/step6_orchestrator_quixbugs_v5_attempts.py \
    --tasks_path data/quixbugs_tasks_v2.jsonl \
    --task_index "$i" \
    --llama_path /usr/local/bin/llama-completion \
    --gguf_model_path models/gguf/qwen2.5-coder-1.5b-instruct-q4_k_m.gguf \
    --max_attempts 3 \
    --slm_timeout_s 400 \
    --fallback_model gpt-4.1 \
    --fallback_max_attempts 2
done
```

Run artifacts location:
- `episodes/quixbugs_runs/attempts/<timestamp>_<algo>/...`

