## 2) HumanEval (Latest = v2) - Script Arguments and How Experiments Were Run

Script:
- `src/humaneval/run_humaneval_hybrid_v2.py`

Task selection arguments:
- `--tasks_path` (default `data/external/humaneval/humaneval_train.jsonl`)
- `--task_index` (default `-1`)
- `--task_id` (default empty string)
- `--max_tasks` (default `-1`)

SLM generation arguments:
- `--llama_path` (default `/usr/local/bin/llama-completion` or env `LLAMA_COMPLETION`)
- `--gguf_model_path` (default `models/gguf/qwen2.5-coder-1.5b-instruct-q4_k_m.gguf`)
- `--max_new_tokens` (default `256`)
- `--slm_timeout_s` (default `120`)
- `--slm_attempts` (default `2`)

Evaluation/routing arguments:
- `--test_timeout_s` (default `5`)
- `--pass_threshold` (default `1.0`)

Fallback LLM arguments:
- `--fallback_attempts` (default `1`)
- `--fallback_model` (default `gpt-4.2`)
- `--fallback_timeout_s` (default `120`)
- `--fallback_max_tokens` (default `512`)
- `--fallback_temp` (default `0.0`)

RAG and self-debug arguments:
- `--rag_enabled` (default `0`)
- `--rag_top_k` (default `3`)
- `--self_debug_enabled` (default `1`)
- `--self_debug_max_tokens` (default `128`)

Output argument:
- `--out_dir` (default `episodes/humaneval_runs`)

Typical experiment run (single task by ID):
```bash
python src/humaneval/run_humaneval_hybrid_v2.py \
  --tasks_path data/external/humaneval/humaneval_train.jsonl \
  --task_id HumanEval/8 \
  --llama_path /usr/local/bin/llama-completion \
  --gguf_model_path models/gguf/qwen2.5-coder-1.5b-instruct-q4_k_m.gguf \
  --slm_attempts 2 \
  --fallback_attempts 2 \
  --fallback_model gpt-4o-mini \
  --rag_enabled 1 \
  --self_debug_enabled 1 \
  --out_dir episodes/humaneval_runs
```

Typical experiment run (single task by index):
```bash
python src/humaneval/run_humaneval_hybrid_v2.py \
  --tasks_path data/external/humaneval/humaneval_train.jsonl \
  --task_index 8 \
  --slm_attempts 2 \
  --fallback_attempts 2
```

Typical full sweep pattern:
```bash
python src/humaneval/run_humaneval_hybrid_v2.py \
  --tasks_path data/external/humaneval/humaneval_train.jsonl \
  --max_tasks -1 \
  --slm_attempts 2 \
  --fallback_attempts 2 \
  --out_dir episodes/humaneval_runs
```

Run artifacts location:
- `episodes/humaneval_runs/<timestamp>_HumanEval_<id>/...`
- Global summary: `episodes/humaneval_runs/runs_summary.jsonl`

